    <h1>Voice of Customer (VoC)</h1>
    <p class="description">The structured process of capturing what customers truly want, expect, and complain about — then using those insights to improve <strong>product, positioning, and copy</strong>. The companies that grow fastest are those whose marketing sounds like their customers, not their marketing team.</p>
    <div class="post-meta">
